title: 02/09/21 DPS Best OF
itunes:title: 02/09/21 DPS Best OF
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, we continue to recap Super Bowl LV. Former Pro Bowl Offensive Lineman Tony Boselli calls in to discuss what surprised him about the Chiefs game plan on Sunday. Seahawks QB Russell Wilson answers questions about some of the reports surrounding his future in Seattle. And Nick Wright of FS1's First Things First joins us after his prediction gone wrong that the Chiefs would win by 2 scores.
